procstep.procdesc: Robert Edwards gathered source materials from NYDoH, MDE, and PADEP and created a spreadsheet with only Basin related advisories.

fish consumption.xls was used to select the appropriate stream reaches from the National Hydrography Dataset (NHD). The EventMaker tool was used to create the correct stream reaches from the NHD The resulting feature class was exported into a new shapefile called fish_cnsmp.shp. All fields from fish consumption.xls were added to the attribute table.
Updated shapefile with new or modified advisories on 9/29/2011.

dataqual.logic: Fish consumption advisories were provided as a text description and streams were taken from the NHD using Event Maker based on those descriptions.
dataqual.complete: All fish consumption advisories within the Susquehanna River Basin as of September 29, 2011.
